<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 28 at 1:30PM CST  by NWS QuadCities</headline>
<description>...Light to Moderate Snow This Afternoon and Evening...
Snow will bring reduced visibilities and a few slick spots on area
roads this afternoon and evening. Most of the accumulation will
occur on elevated and grassy surfaces. If traveling, slow down and
leave plenty of distance in front of you and the next vehicle.
In addition, ice may occur on bridges and overpasses late this
evening, as temperatures drop to near freezing this evening.</description>
